These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, writer, designer, freelancer, architect, bartender
City: rome, paris, marseilles, london, boston, venice, nizza
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, old-henry, fonseca, game, bongani, montecristo, vegafina
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, colombian, brazilian, malaysian, egyptian, american, dutch
 1. the dressmaker is on the left of the bartender##1
 2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the italian is the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the designer##1
 8. the colombian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the architect is in the middle##1
12. the writer is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
14. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
15. the dutch is on the left of the dressmaker##1
16. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
17. the american is on the right of the dutch##1
18. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the game-smoker##1
19. the brazilian is in the middle##1
20. the game-smoker is on the left of the fisherman##1
21. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Job      | writer    | dressmaker     | bartender  | architect   | designer | freelancer      | fisherman          |
| City   | nizza    | london   | venice  | boston       | rome  | paris      | marseilles     |
